last_episode_to_air.name: Well Boys, I Guess I Gotta Get Dead
last_episode_to_air.overview: The good times are killing them: A bank error in their favor sends the boys on a spending spree. When the cops arrive, Ricky must fake his own death.

name: Trailer Park Boys: The Animated Series
original_name: Trailer Park Boys: The Animated Series
overview: Nova Scotia’s favorite miscreants have always been super sketchy. Now, carrying on from the Season 12 finale, the boys have become complete cartoons.

episodes.name: Long Story Short... A Bear Ripped My Cock Off and Ate It
episodes.overview: Back in jail, tripping on mushrooms and transformed into cartoons, the boys test the limits of their new reality with both fear and excitement.

episodes.name: The Pepperoni Cobra
episodes.overview: A tapeworm is taking the grub right out of Ricky's mouth, but when the parasite swipes his weed, that's the last straw. Bubbles connects at the club.

episodes.name: The Stanley Bong
episodes.overview: Bubbles convinces Julian and Ricky to join him as he stalks Wayne Gretzky. Now they must beat the Moncton Mudslides to win back the Stanley Bong.

episodes.name: The Penis Milker
episodes.overview: The boys go on a mission to save a mountain lion friend, but they don't count on the mosquitoes, bear traps or sperm-harvesting backwoods locals.

episodes.name: Big Ho's Carwash
episodes.overview: Business booms -- and chaos reigns -- as Julian revs up a sexy car wash, Ricky opens a trailer pool, and Bubbles goes it alone to build his dream shed.

episodes.name: The Three Mustardteers
episodes.overview: Old-school hash brings back memories of grade school, when young Julian, Ricky and Bubbles met, smoked and retaliated against a bully with a pellet gun.

episodes.name: Satan's Bastards
episodes.overview: Trinity and Jacob want to move, so the boys deliver hash to raise cash. But Ricky gets greedy and incurs the wrath of a rampaging biker gang.

episodes.name: Space Weed
episodes.overview: When Ricky's grow operations are exposed, an entrepreneur approaches him to cultivate dope in space. Beyond pumped, Bubbles demands to join the team.

episodes.name: Hurricane Ricky
episodes.overview: To get off the grid, Ricky liberates hundreds of car batteries. Julian concocts a scheme to ride out a big storm, but Mother Nature has other plans.

episodes.name: Trailerstock
episodes.overview: The boys throw a benefit concert featuring Helix to save Sunnyvale. But how can their event compete with the nearby Queens of the Stone Age show?

episodes.name: Duber
episodes.overview: Ride-sharing hits a new high when Ricky attempts to go legit with a dope-smoking twist on Uber: Duber. But can the gang handle success — and Randy?

episodes.name: Viral Video
episodes.overview: The viral video cash-in is on. Ricky kidnaps a rank clown for Mo’s birthday party. But when the bozo bails, Cory and Randy step up as party starters.

episodes.name: The Tax Man F**ked Me
episodes.overview: Sunnyvale’s sketchiest get scammed by grifters posing as tax agents. A trap is set, then lethal farts lead the boys to a familiar face.

episodes.name: Scamazon
episodes.overview: Bubbles pours his life savings into Kitty Shakes while Julian and Ricky drive off to steal packages. Later, a reality competition comes calling.

episodes.name: Clint Eatswood
episodes.overview: The gang must rustle up dough to cure Bubbles’s kitten of hookworms, even if that means becoming movie stars. But are the boys ready to play dirty?

episodes.name: The First Time We Smoked Weed
episodes.overview: The fellas take a shady trip down memory lane back to 1979: the first time they smoked Panama Red — and launched a life of petty crime.

episodes.name: Bubbles for Mayor
episodes.overview: The city rounds up Bubbles’s free-range kitties, and when the mayor kicks him to the curb, he decides to run for office. One paradigm shift coming up.

episodes.name: The Bagshank Redemption
episodes.overview: After going to jail for peeing on the cops, Ricky claims he’s turning over a new leaf. That means ditching his pals to go on a Costco treasure hunt.

episodes.name: The F**ket List
episodes.overview: Bubbles drags Julian to the fair to cheer him up. After a fortuneteller delivers the bad news, the guys end up in a cult. Time to start drinking.
